13:06.350 --> 13:08.880
I was just,uh,I was dropping off my time card.

13:08.960 --> 13:10.260
Great.I'm heading out.

13:10.340 --> 13:13.410
Could you call marco to confirm the vineyard tours for next month?

13:13.490 --> 13:14.780
Yeah,sure.

13:15.070 --> 13:17.130
Hey,guys.Uh,sorry.A little problem.

13:17.130 --> 13:20.180
I just realized I'm not gonna be able to go to the vineyard with you today.

13:20.260 --> 13:22.280
I have a long-standing dinner with saul.

13:22.380 --> 13:25.570
Tommy,that meeting has been on the books for weeks.

13:25.630 --> 13:28.450
