13:28.530 --> 13:30.040
Yeah,but rebecca can go with you.

13:30.120 --> 13:31.170
She's got a great eye.

13:31.230 --> 13:34.590
Yeah,I'm sure she'd really appreciate you pawning your work off on her.

13:34.670 --> 13:36.310
No,you know,actually,I-I wouldn't mind.

13:36.410 --> 13:37.760
