14:47.480 --> 14:49.000
-That was me. -Yes,that was you.

14:49.080 --> 14:50.680
I loved that umbrella.

14:50.760 --> 14:52.300
You just have to stay...

14:52.380 --> 14:54.320
open to the moments.

14:54.650 --> 14:57.450
But,sarah,you're not wrong for wanting to go back to work.

14:57.530 --> 14:59.920
