15:43.840 --> 15:45.060
okay.

15:45.140 --> 15:46.490
Okay.

15:48.520 --> 15:51.000
I've gotta say,youre a natural.

15:51.080 --> 15:52.510
You have a great eye.

15:52.580 --> 15:53.870
