16:33.210 --> 16:36.830
Which I know sounds crazy,since he was keeping me from nora.

16:36.910 --> 16:38.470
No,no,that doesn't sound crazy.

16:38.550 --> 16:41.550
I mean,I don't know how I would feel if I was in your shoes,so...

16:42.410 --> 16:44.190
actually...

16:44.270 --> 16:47.160
I thought about finding him.

16:47.360 --> 16:50.440
I even went so far as to look him up.

16:50.490 --> 16:52.470
He lives in bakersfield.

16:54.960 --> 16:56.070
Have you met him?

16:56.150 --> 16:57.880
