18:04.660 --> 18:06.170
So how's julia?

18:06.390 --> 18:07.380
She's better.

18:07.460 --> 18:11.350
You know,I mean,uh,elizabeth is a lot of work.

18:12.050 --> 18:14.040
What about holly?How's all that going?

18:14.100 --> 18:15.690
Not a conflict to speak of.

18:15.790 --> 18:17.620
