18:28.340 --> 18:29.720
Let me fill your glass for you.

18:29.780 --> 18:31.130
Okay.

18:32.010 --> 18:33.240
So...

18:33.340 --> 18:34.950
you and justin.

18:36.010 --> 18:38.150
Come on.We opened a bottle of wine.

18:38.160 --> 18:40.020
Let's put it to good use.

18:40.460 --> 18:42.150
Is it serious?

18:42.470 --> 18:44.210
Yeah,I think so.

18:44.330 --> 18:45.980
I mean,we hang out all the time.

18:46.060 --> 18:48.660
We...have so much fun together.

18:50.380 --> 18:52.450
I'm sensing a "but.

18:52.570 --> 18:54.560
" No,it--it's just that...

